      <title>白俄罗斯与柏林就德国男子被判处死刑一事进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/belarus-in-talks-with-berlin-over-german-man-sentenced-to-death</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白俄罗斯和德国正在就一名德国公民的命运进行谈判，该公民被明斯克指控为乌克兰雇佣兵并被判处死刑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/belarus-in-talks-with-berlin-over-german-man-sentenced-to-death</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 14:48:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
